cu_modifications.explanation: Setting remote_s_address to an unreachable IP '10.0.0.1' will cause connection failure in the front-haul interface, preventing proper communication between CU and DU.
cu_modifications.explanation_zh: 將 remote_s_address 設定為無法連線的 IP '10.0.0.1' 會導致前傳介面的連線失敗，阻止 CU 和 DU 之間的正常通訊。

du_modifications.explanation: Changing absoluteFrequencySSB from 641280 to 640008 causes frequency misalignment, leading to synchronization issues in the SSB transmission and potential cell search failures.
du_modifications.explanation_zh: 將 absoluteFrequencySSB 從 641280 更改為 640008 會導致頻率錯位，造成 SSB 傳輸中的同步問題，並可能導致小區搜尋失敗。
